snippet.title: Cozy Guest
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel.

Here you will see a compilation of Saint Row game tutorials, for making non-fictitious/fantasy characters. This can be anything from TV show celebrities, movie characters to video game characters.

If you have any requests for a character you would like to see, I am open to suggestions.

Thanks for stopping by.


Q&A Section


Q. Can you do Harry Potter?

A. Yes, but his trade mark glasses will not be possible. Daniel Radcliffe would be the closest I can get.


Q. Can you do (this person), (this person), (that person) and (this person) please?

A. I could do, but the person who requests after you has a longer time to wait. So I prefer one request at a time.


Q. Why is this in my recommendations? 

A. Maybe because my tags were broad enough to reach more people. Sorry if I offended you. Please simply just click on the "not interested" option, next to the thumbnail.


Q. Can you create yourself?

A. Possibly. But I am not ready to show myself yet.
